ys <MOTION> <CHARACTER> -- adds surrounding characters
ds <CHARACTER> -- deletes surrounding characters
cs <FROM CHARACTER> <To CHARACTER> -- Change surrounding characters

yw -- copy(yank) word
grw -- replace word with clipboard buffer

gcc -- (un)comment line
gc3j -- (un)comment 3 lines 

space + e -- open/close file explorer
a -- add file in the explorer

Telescope
Ctrl + k - move to prev selection
Ctrl + j - move to next selection
Ctrl + q - send items to quick fix list

Find ei t66ta miski p2rast
Space + ff -- find file
Space + fs -- find string
Space + fc -- find current string the cursor is on
Space + fb -- find string in the active buffer
Space + fh -- show help tags


